Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows Defender\MpEngine
and add/ change the DWORD string
MpEnablePus
to
1


Or enter this command in powershell, started with admin rights:
Set-MpPreference -PUAProtection Enabled


Finish. No reboot required.

Here a test site from Microsoft: https://demo.wd.microsoft.com/Page/PUA
